title: Tom Brady joins wellness company Aescape, bringing his longevity protocols to massage robots
summary: Tom Brady struck a partnership with robotic massage device maker Aescape to provide the company with exclusive rights to his recovery and longevity protocols.

title: Trump administration reportedly plans to link autism to Tylenol ingredient use in pregnancy
summary: Federal health officials also are expected to highlight leucovorin, a form of folate, as a potential autism treatment, according to The Washington Post.
